4
00:00:42,475 --> 00:00:43,942
I'm just glad you're here.

5
00:00:43,943 --> 00:00:45,111
You like me?

6
00:00:47,113 --> 00:00:47,914
Not bad.

7
00:00:47,915 --> 00:00:49,149
They did a great job.

8
00:00:49,682 --> 00:00:51,483
This level of intimacy is fine, right?

9
00:00:51,484 --> 00:00:51,951
Yeah.

10
00:00:51,951 --> 00:00:52,951
No problem.

11
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:55,054
We're back!

12
00:00:55,588 --> 00:00:56,356
Did anything happen

13
00:00:56,357 --> 00:00:57,657
that I should know about?

14
00:00:58,591 --> 00:00:59,592
I don't think so.

15
00:00:59,859 --> 00:01:00,827
I just reviewed the footage.

16
00:01:00,827 --> 00:01:01,528
It all looks pretty good.

17
00:01:01,529 --> 00:01:02,529
Nice work.

18
00:01:04,497 --> 00:01:05,931
How did I never notice before

19
00:01:05,932 --> 00:01:07,200
