20
00:01:07,567 --> 00:01:08,401
That's because before,

21
00:01:08,402 --> 00:01:09,802
I didn't have anyone to look after.

22
00:01:13,573 --> 00:01:15,441
As for the shoot the day after tomorrow,

23
00:01:15,442 --> 00:01:17,202
I'll need you two to
stay in this headspace.

24
00:01:17,477 --> 00:01:18,577
And don't post anything

25
00:01:18,578 --> 00:01:19,512
