26
00:01:19,512 --> 00:01:20,413
Let's keep the mystery alive.

27
00:01:20,413 --> 00:01:20,847
Got it.

28
00:01:20,847 --> 00:01:21,614
Good work today.

29
00:01:21,615 --> 00:01:22,749
Thanks, everyone.

30
00:01:23,316 --> 00:01:23,950
Let's go.

31
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:25,250
Time to head back.

32
00:01:28,474 --> 00:01:29,474
Hei Yan.

33
00:01:31,157 --> 00:01:32,692
We finally built some chemistry,

34
00:01:33,726 --> 00:01:35,194
so don't go home and forget it all

35
00:01:35,195 --> 00:01:37,163
