36
00:01:44,971 --> 00:01:45,971
Bye!

37
00:01:47,841 --> 00:01:49,042
Let's go. Weren't we leaving?

38
00:01:57,984 --> 00:01:59,051
Didn't I warn you

39
00:01:59,052 --> 00:02:00,820
